K8

https://www.oreilly.com/ideas/how-to-manage-docker-containers-in-kubernetes-with-java

https://kubernetes.io/docs/setup/learning-environment/minikube/

https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/tools/install-kubectl/

https://github.com/tamilsng/oreilly-docker-java-shopping


docker build -t tamil/djshopfront:1.0 .

docker push tamil/djshopfront:1.0

docker build -t tamil/djproductcatalogue:1.0 .

docker push tamil/djproductcatalogue:1.0

docker build -t tamil/djstockmanager:1.0 .

docker push tamil/djstockmanager:1.0



Kubernates folder


minikube start --cpus 2 --memory 4096

kubectl apply -f shopfront-service.yaml

kubectl apply -f productcatalogue-service.yaml

kubectl apply -f stockmanager-service.yaml

kubectl get svc

kubectl get pods

curl $(minikube service shopfront --url)/health

minikube service shopfront

